---
title: Mediterranean Lamb Couscous Bowl with Salsa, Pickled Onion & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Introduce your tastebuds to the incredible flavour of garlic and herb infused lamb; it really packs a punch. Sitting on a hearty bed of couscous and topped with Greek-style yoghurt, this dish offers a depth of flavour that's sure to knock your socks off.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
